com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.retentionrule

Class RetentionRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.ExtensibleObject
      • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.retentionrule.RetentionRule

  • public class RetentionRule
extends ExtensibleObject
    RetentionRules govern after what time old data is to be removed from the cloud. Each type of document can have its own rule, so that some types can be kept longer, while others get cleaned up faster.
